HEADWORD: dyslectic
<hw>dyslectic</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Suffering from dyslexia; having
impaired ability to comprehend written words; a condition usually
associated with a neurologic disorder.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> dyslexic.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

